            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35903156">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“我们要比敌人活得更长久。”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-08-16 23:52</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                “我们要比敌人活得更长久。”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







